patches only status\n221: - [ ] GET ...?watch=true streams NDJSON\n222: \n223: ### CodeInterpreter CRUD API (AR-004-030 to 037)\n224: - [ ] Same patterns as AgentRuntime CRUD\n225: \n226: ### Middleware & Observability (AR-004-040 to 042)\n227: - [ ] Request logging middleware logs method, path, status, latency\n228: - [ ] Metrics collection tracks request count, duration histogram\n229: - [ ] Error handling maps K8s errors to HTTP status codes\n230: \n231: ### API Format & Compatibility (AR-004-050 to 051)\n232: - [ ] Content-Type: application/json for requests/responses\n233: - [ ] Error responses follow Kubernetes Status format\n234: \n235: ### Integration with client-go (AR-004-060 to 062)\n236: - [ ] Uses RuntimeV1alpha1 Clientset accessor\n237: - [ ] Uses Informers for list operations (when cache ready)\n238: - [ ] Uses Listers for cached reads\n239: \n240: ---\n241: \n242: ## Dependencies\n243: \n244: | Task | Depends On |\n245: |------|------------|\n246: | Phase 2 | Phase 1 |\n247: | Phase 3 | Phase 2 |\n248: | Phase 4 | Phase 2 |\n249: | Phase 5 | Phase 2, 3, 4 |\n250: | Phase 6 | Phase 2 |\n251: | Phase 7 | Phase 4, 5, 6 |\n252: | Phase 8 | Phase 7 |\n253: | Phase 9 | Phase 5, 6 |\n254: | Phase 10 | Phase 7, 9 |\n255: | Phase 11 | Phase 9, 10 |\n256: \n257: ---\n258: \n259: ## References\n260: \n261: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-004/delta-spec.md`\n262: - client-go: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n263: - AgentRuntime CRD: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n264: - CodeInterpreter CRD: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n265: - API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n\n(End of file - total 265 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-004 — WorkloadManager HTTP 服务框架 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Directory Scaffold\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/` directory structure\n- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` - API request/re